messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com
Struggling with pornography or sexual addiction? We're here to offer guidance and prayer. How can we assist you today? Would you like to share a specific prayer request?

Heavenly Father, we come before you today, seeking your protection and guidance. We pray against the spirit of untimely death, asking for your divine intervention in our lives. We renounce any spirit of pride that may lead us away from your path and ask for humility to fill our hearts.
